### GET published events sorted by startDate
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=status eq 'Published'&$orderby=startDate asc

### GET events filtered by type Workshop
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=eventType eq 'Workshop'

### GET all registrations for a specific event
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations?$filter=event_ID eq 'ev111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000001'

### POST a new registration
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_ID": "ev111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
  "attendeeName": "Arjun Das",
  "attendeeEmail": "arjun@gmail.com",
  "attendeePhone": "+91-9800000011",
  "company": "NewCo",
  "ticketType": "General",
  "registrationDate": "2024-06-20",
  "status": "Confirmed",
  "amountPaid": 500.00,
  "paymentId": "PAY011"
}

### GET speakers sorted by rating descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Speakers?$orderby=rating desc

### GET events with available seats
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=registeredCount lt maxAttendees

### PATCH event status to Published
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events(ev111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000004)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Published"
}

### POST feedback for an event
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_ID": "ev111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "attendeeEmail": "deepak@gmail.com",
  "overallRating": 4.5,
  "contentRating": 4.8,
  "venueRating": 4.2,
  "speakerRating": 4.7,
  "comment": "Great event overall!",
  "submittedAt": "2024-07-12T10:00:00"
}